    <item>
      <title>特朗普赢得华尔街亿万富翁的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/trump-earns-backing-of-wall-street-billionaires-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在美国历史上首次对前总统的刑事审判中被判有罪。然而，越来越多的美国商界和金融界知名人士纷纷支持特朗普竞选总统。安玛丽·霍登在今天的“Big Take”中详细介绍了详情。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/trump-earns-backing-of-wall-street-billionaires-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 10:28:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国个人消费支出报告预览：值得关注的事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/us-pce-report-preview-what-to-watch-for-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[核心个人消费支出价格指数是美联储衡量潜在通胀的首选指标，4 月份该指数可能放缓至今年以来的最低月度涨幅。个人支出和收入预计也将放缓。迈克尔·麦基 (Michael McKee) 在彭博电视上进行了预告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/us-pce-report-preview-what-to-watch-for-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 10:12:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本上月干预支出创纪录 620 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/japan-spent-record-62-billion-in-past-month-on-yen-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日元兑美元汇率跌至 34 年来的最低点后，日本上个月花费了创纪录的 9.8 万亿日元（622 亿美元）来支撑日元，超过了 2022 年为捍卫日元而投入的资金量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/japan-spent-record-62-billion-in-past-month-on-yen-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 10:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲开发银行称非洲无力承担 750 亿美元的利息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/africa-can-ill-afford-75-billion-interest-payments-afdb-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据非洲开发银行称，非洲国家今年将花费 750 亿美元偿还债务利息，这些资金急需用于解决社会支出和公共投资等紧迫问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/africa-can-ill-afford-75-billion-interest-payments-afdb-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 10:02:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国要求债券承销商检查地方债务风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/china-asks-bond-underwriters-to-check-for-local-debt-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻看到的一份通知显示，中国市场监管机构本周要求一些金融公司审查任何可能违反政府化解地方债务风险计划的债券承销活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/china-asks-bond-underwriters-to-check-for-local-debt-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 09:53:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家史蒂芬·罗奇称美国面临与中国“永远”的贸易战的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/us-risks-a-forever-trade-war-with-china-stephen-roach-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济学家史蒂芬·罗奇批评美国针对中国的贸易政策是一个“错误”，有可能引发两国之间无休止的经济冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/us-risks-a-forever-trade-war-with-china-stephen-roach-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 09:53:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
